ion would have been the 23rd largest population in the world.\", \"from\": 8018, \"to\": 8112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8040, \"end\": 8054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Nation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Refugee Nation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Nation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Nation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a country\", \"from\": 8029, \"to\": 8038}, {\"ngram\": \"the 23rd largest population\", \"from\": 8071, \"to\": 8098}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 8102, \"to\": 8111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By the time of the Tokyo games in 2021, Refugee Nation had grown to82 millionand was then the 20th largest in the world, situated just between Thailand and Germany.\", \"from\": 8114, \"to\": 8278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8133, \"end\": 8138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999977712832, \"rank\": 2.2281799329860616e-09, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 8154, \"end\": 8168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Nation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Refugee Nation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Nation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Nation\"}, {\"begin\": 8257, \"end\": 8265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\", \"score\": 0.9999988551382745, \"rank\": 1.1438675221330118e-06, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\"}, {\"begin\": 8270, \"end\": 8277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.9925919301079459, \"rank\": 0.007260311871192897, \"text\": \"Germany\"