\", \"from\": 8911, \"to\": 8927}, {\"ngram\": \"the resulting escalation\", \"from\": 8932, \"to\": 8956}, {\"ngram\": \"forced migration\", \"from\": 8960, \"to\": 8976}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S. economic sanctions\", \"from\": 9029, \"to\": 9052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two years before the Rio Olympics, theUN Human Rights Councilexpressed alarm at \\\"the disproportionate and indiscriminate human costs of unilateral sanctions and their negative effects on the civilian population.\\\"\", \"from\": 9054, \"to\": 9266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9075, \"end\": 9087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0783716305115296e-16, \"text\": \"Rio Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theUN Human Rights Councilexpressed alarm\", \"from\": 9089, \"to\": 9130}, {\"ngram\": \"the disproportionate and indiscriminate human costs\", \"from\": 9135, \"to\": 9186}, {\"ngram\": \"unilateral sanctions\", \"from\": 9190, \"to\": 9210}, {\"ngram\": \"their negative effects\", \"from\": 9215, \"to\": 9237}, {\"ngram\": \"the civilian population\", \"from\": 9241, \"to\": 9264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Iran, for example, the U.S. imposed extreme sanctions in 2018 when then-PresidentDonald Trumppulled out of the Iran nuclear deal despite recognition by theUN's nuclear watchdog agencythatTehranwas in compliance with the deal's requirements.\", \"from\": 9268, \"to\": 9511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9271, \"end\": 9275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"score\": 0.9978657916918282, \"rank\": 0.001818227976205694, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\"}, {\"begin\": 9382, \"end\": 9399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joint_Comprehensive_Plan_of_Action\"