, \"from\": 15869, \"to\": 15976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15938, \"end\": 15943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9994375230682253, \"rank\": 0.000562793415417102, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 37 athletes\", \"from\": 15869, \"to\": 15884}, {\"ngram\": \"audiences\", \"from\": 15893, \"to\": 15902}, {\"ngram\": \"their feet\", \"from\": 15906, \"to\": 15916}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 15921, \"to\": 15930}, {\"ngram\": \"screens\", \"from\": 15951, \"to\": 15958}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 15966, \"to\": 15975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the triumph and beauty of the Refugee Team, and all that these young people have accomplished despite having been forced to leave their homes, cannot hide the stark reality that mass displacement on a global scale has become the new normal.\", \"from\": 15977, \"to\": 16221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16011, \"end\": 16023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Refugee Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the triumph\", \"from\": 15981, \"to\": 15992}, {\"ngram\": \"beauty\", \"from\": 15997, \"to\": 16003}, {\"ngram\": \"these young people\", \"from\": 16038, \"to\": 16056}, {\"ngram\": \"their homes\", \"from\": 16111, \"to\": 16122}, {\"ngram\": \"the stark reality\", \"from\": 16136, \"to\": 16153}, {\"ngram\": \"a global scale\", \"from\": 16180, \"to\": 16194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And whatever the specific conditions that forced each of them to leave their homes, U.S. policy is one of the factors that made things worse in their countries.\", \"from\": 16222, \"to\": 16382, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the specific conditions\", \"from\": 16235, \"to\": 16258}, {\"ngram\": \"their homes\", \"from\": 16293, \"to\": 16304}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S. policy\", \"from\": 16306, \"to\": 16317}, {\"ngram\": \"the factors\", \"from\": 16328, \"to\": 16339}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 16350, \"to\": 16356}, {\"ngram\": \"their countries\", \"from\": 16366, \"to\": 16381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Providing world-class athletes dispossessed from their homes a chance to compete in the Olympic games is a gift-to them and their communities, and to the rest of us watching and cheering them on.\", \"from\": 16384, \"to\": 16579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"world-class athletes\", \"from\": 16394, \"to\": 16414}, {\"ngram\": \"their homes\", \"from\": 16433, \"to\": 16444}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 16445, \"to\": 16453}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic games\", \"from\": 16468, \"to\": 16485}, {\"ngram\": \"a gift\", \"from\": 16489, \"to\": 16495}, {\"ngram\": \"their communities\", \"from\": 16508, \"to\": 16525}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 16534, \"to\": 16542}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 16546, \"to\": 16548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But at the end of the day, the need for such a team speaks to our failure-to stop the normalization of forced displacement, and to reverse the conditions that create it in the first place.\", \"from\": 16580, \"to\": 16768, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 16587, \"to\": 16594}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 16598, \"to\": 16605}, {\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 16607, \"to\": 16615}, {\"ngram\": \"such a team\", \"from\": 16620, \"to\": 16631}, {\"ngram\": \"our failure\", \"from\": 16642, \"to\": 16653}, {\"ngram\": \"the normalization\", \"from\": 16662, \"to\": 16679}, {\"ngram\": \"forced displacement\", \"from\": 16683, \"to\": 16702}, {\"ngram\": \"the conditions\", \"from\": 16719, \"to\": 16733}, {\"ngram\": \"the first place\", \"from\": 16752, \"to\": 16767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Including ending U.S. economic sanctions.\", \"from\": 16769, \"to\": 16810, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"U.S. economic sanctions\", \"from\": 16786, \"to\": 16809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The chance to win a medal in Paris is great-but would not it be better if these amazing athletes could instead win the right to return safely home instead?\", \"from\": 16811, \"to\": 16966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16840, \"end\": 16845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999758984, \"rank\": 2.391063944289441e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The chance\", \"from\": 16811, \"to\": 16821}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 16829, \"to\": 16836}, {\"ngram\": \"these amazing athletes\", \"from\": 16885, \"to\": 16907}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 16926, \"to\": 16935}]}]}"